  ggplot(aes(x = pH)) +
  geom_histogram(aes(y = ..density..)) +
  stat_function(fun = dnorm(x = 7.1:7.6, mean = mean(Secondary_Samples$pH), sd = sd(Secondary_Samples$pH)))
  facet_grid(~ Ambient.Or.OAH)
